# Stonecreek Instagram Posts — Master Guide

This is the index. When asked to make a post, pick the archetype that fits the content, then read its detailed guide in `archetypes/`.

**Always:** 1080 × 1350 (4:5 portrait). Lowercase except for God / Jesus / Lord / Holy Spirit and proper nouns. Recoleta for display, Helvetica Neue for body/UI, brand color tokens only.

---

## Pick the archetype

| If the content is… | Use archetype | File |
|---|---|---|
| A short pastor or scripture quote, no photo available | **01 · Quote (minimal)** | `archetypes/01_quote_minimal.md` |
| A scripture passage longer than ~10 words | **02 · Scripture (textured)** | `archetypes/02_scripture_textured.md` |
| A pastor quote, photo of the moment is available | **03 · Quote over photo** | `archetypes/03_quote_over_photo.md` |
| Sermon clip / longer pull-quote with the speaker visible | **04 · Sermon pull-quote** | `archetypes/04_sermon_pullquote.md` |
| Promoting an event, class, or program | **05 · Event announcement** | `archetypes/05_event_announcement.md` |
| Sub-brand identity post (KIDS / YTH big logo over photo) | **06 · Sub-brand hero** | `archetypes/06_subbrand_hero.md` |

